Parser combinator librariy

Types

ParseResult[Val] = object
  mark: string
  case success*: bool
  of true:
      value*: Val
      endpos*: int

  of false:
      error*: string

  
Callbacks = object
  entry*: proc (pos: int)
  success*: proc (pos: int)
  failure*: proc (pos: int)

Parser[Val; Buf] = proc (buffer: Buf; position: int = 0): ParseResult[Val]

Consts

noCallbacks = (entry: (:anonymous, nil), success: (:anonymous, nil),
             failure: (:anonymous, nil))
